settings.custom_liquid:
{% if product.metafields.custom.details.value == blank %} 
 {{ product.description }}
{% endif %}
 {% if product.metafields.custom.details != blank %}

<ul class="nav nav-tabs">
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a href="#description" class="nav-link active" data-bs-toggle="tab">Description</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a href="#details" class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab">Details</a>
    </li>
    <li class="nav-item">
        <a href="#socialgood" class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab">Social Good</a>
    </li>

 <li class="nav-item">
        <a href="#development" class="nav-link" data-bs-toggle="tab">Development</a>
    </li>
</ul>
<div class="tab-content">
    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="description">
        {{ product.description }}

    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="details">
        {{ product.metafields.custom.details | metafield_tag }}
    </div>
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="socialgood">
        <style>
              img.mikeIcon {
                height: 75px;
                width: 75px;
              }
              .tooltip {
                position: relative;
                display: inline-block;

              }

              .tooltip .tooltiptext {
                visibility: hidden;
                width: 250px;
                background-color: #4A4F55;
                color: #E8E2BF;
                text-align: center;
                border-radius: 6px;
                padding: 5px;

                /* Position the tooltip */
                position: absolute;
                z-index: 1;
                bottom: 100%;
                left: 50%;
                margin-left: -60px;
              }

              .tooltip:hover .tooltiptext {
                visibility: visible;
              }
            </style>

            {% if product.tags contains 'Made in USA' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/07_MADE-IN-USA.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    This product was manufactured in the U.S.A.
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if product.tags contains 'Social Good' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/04_SOCIAL-GOOD.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    This vendor contributes a portion of sales to social good.  Whether it be cleaning trash or providing food or clothing to children in need, this manufacturer is giving back.
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if product.tags contains 'Eco-Friendly' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/03_ECO-FRIENDLY.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    This product is eco friendly.  Recycled plastics, natural wood with water based dyes, and/or organic materials were used to develop this product.
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if product.tags contains 'Handmade' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/02_HANDMADE.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    This product was hand made.  Seriously.
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.tags contains 'Made in Colorado' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/06_MADE-IN-COLORADO.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    Proudly made in colorful Colorado!
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.tags contains 'Woman Owned' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/15_WOMAN-OWNED.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    The company that makes this product is Woman Owned.
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.tags contains 'Not on Amazon' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/11_NOT-ON-AMAZON.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                    We are not supporting a hot dog shaped rocket owning billionaire with this one, this product cannot be found on Amazon.
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.tags contains 'Organic' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/01_ORGANIC.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                Certified Organic in the house.             
              </div>            
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.tags contains 'Small Batch' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/10_SMALL-BATCH.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                This product was produced in small batches.         
              </div>            
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if product.tags contains 'Fair Trade' %}

            <div class="tooltip">
                <img class="mikeIcon" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/05_FAIR-TRADE-CERTIFIED.png" />
                <div class="tooltiptext">
                  <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0579/1678/4840/files/FairTrade.png" width="50px" />
                When you see a product with the Fair Trade Certified seal, you can be sure it meets rigorous social, environmental, and economic standards. That means:
                  <ul>
                    <li>Safe working conditions</li>
                    <li>Environmental protection</li>
                    <li>Sustainable livelihoods</li>
                    <li>Community Development Funds</li>    
                  </ul>
              </div>            
            </div>
            {% endif %}

        </div>

    <div class="tab-pane fade show" id="development">
<p>
You want to provide your kiddo with the tools they need to thrive, but also keep it real, because let's face it, raising kids never strictly adheres to the script.  All of our toys are curated by an early childhood development expert and mother of four littles.  Our parenting and development philosphy is influenced by Maria Montessori, Waldorf, and Reggio Emilia, but we don't try to pretend one method is right for everyone.  With over 20 years experience, we've seen it in the field and then at home.  Empower your child with the tools that will help with development, but also spark their interest and most importantly, are super fun!

</p>

    </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endif %}

